				<wikidot:authorName>mlister</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3027978</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This does have some wonderful imagery, but it plays the compulsion effect too straight. Having reread it multiple times to make sure I wasn't missing anything, I can't find much of a narrative arc beyond &quot;Foundation is compelled to do bad stuff, oh no&quot;, and that just isn't satisfying. This feels like a good and compelling (hah) mental image tacked on to a by-the-numbers attempt of the cliches you picked.</p> 
				 	]]>
